        "subject": "LU-5609 libcfs: renamed hlist_add_after to hlist_add_behind",
        "message": "LU-5609 libcfs: renamed hlist_add_after to hlist_add_behind\n\nSince kernel version 3.17 hlist_add_after is renamed to\nhlist_add_behind. It was changed to hlist_add_behind()\nfor causing unconverted code to generate a compile error\ninstead of using the wrong parameter order.\n\nSigned-off-by: Thomas Stibor <t.stibor@gsi.de>\nChange-Id: Ic255cc745066765f2f7eeae2aac96cb3c8701997\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
